setDetails.setDescription: Orticalia is a web3 fund based in isreal. We focus on investing in good long-term crypto projects that have an essential use cause at an early stage, and we also trade micro-cap tokens with our unique trading strategies. You can learn more about it on our website Orticalia.com
setDetails.managerDescription: Yonatan is the CEO and owner of Orticalia Yonatan started trading crypto two years ago full-time after he worked on a crypto projcet called kripton. He made 22.5x on his money in 2021 by trading in microcap tokens. After that, he used the skills he acquired with his six years of experience in the stock market and combined them with his experience trading and working in the crypto market to find suitable long-term projects that solve problems in the crypto market and the world.
